<div id="pf24" class="pf w8 h3" data-page-no="24"><div class="pc pc24 w8 h3"><img class="bi x0 y0 w9 h4" alt="" src="bg24.png"/><div class="t m3f0 x45 h22 y514 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Creation, incarnation and re-creation, the Godhead is at work, and always </div><div class="t m41 x45 h22 y515 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Spirit brings God&apos;s objective to its goal. </div><div class="t m277 x4a h21 y516 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What other special role is filled by the Holy Spirit? 2 Peter 1:20, 21. </div><div class="t m20e x4a h22 y517 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Not only did the Holy Spirit inspire the prophets in producing the Scrip-</div><div class="t m35c x45 h22 y26d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tures but He also has helped people through the ages understand what was </div><div class="t m3f1 x45 h22 y26e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">written. Through His ministry the Scriptures come alive, making Christ real </div><div class="t m35c x45 h22 y26f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to us today, softening our hearts to the Saviour, and enabling us to live for </div><div class="t m3ad x45 h22 y270 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Him. </div><div class="t m234 x45 h21 y53 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SEARCH AND LEARN: What other indications are given of the </div><div class="t m201 x1a h21 y518 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit&apos;s ministry in Old Testament times? </div><div class="t m227 x4a h22 y519 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m3f2 x46 h22 y519 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gen 61 </div><div class="t m8b x3a h22 y493 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m229 xab h22 y493 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m22a x4a h22 y51a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m3f3 x46 h22 y51a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ex. 31</div><div class="t m234 x68 h22 y51a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.</div><div class="t m1e5 x6a h22 y51a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3 </div><div class="t m8b x3a h22 y51a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m229 xab h22 y51a ff5 fsf fc0 sc